## Introduction

Setting up an AI-powered chatbot can sound intimidating, but with ChatFlow AI, even non-technical users can get started quickly. This guide walks you through the setup process step-by-step.

### Step 1: Choose Your Plan

Begin by selecting a plan that fits your business needs. Consider storage, domain support, and feature requirements.

### Step 2: Follow the Onboarding Process

ChatFlow AI's intuitive dashboard guides you through the onboarding process, helping you set up your chatbot in minutes.

### Step 3: Customize Your Chatbot

Adjust the look and feel to match your brand and set up automated responses for common queries.

### Step 4: Integrate with Your Systems

With easy integration options, connect ChatFlow AI with your website, app, or preferred messaging platform without any technical hurdles.

### Step 5: Start Engaging with Customers

Once integrated, start using the chatbot to engage with customers instantly and monitor performance via the analytics dashboard.

## Conclusion

With this guide, setting up ChatFlow AI is a breeze, making it accessible to all businesses regardless of technical expertise.
